The provided sources are insufficient to summarize a current “Chaotic Sanctum dashboard status,” because none appears to be an actual dashboard or status page. The only clearly relevant source describes the **Chaos Sanctuary** from *Diablo II*: Diablo’s inner sanctum is blocked by **five seals**, and the player must open all five to reach the final battle. Three of those seals spawn super-unique enemies—the **Grand Vizier of Chaos**, **Lord De Seis**, and **Infector of Souls**—and once they are defeated and the last seal is opened, the remaining monsters die and **Diablo appears**. [3]

